# OpenScout local environment overrides.
#
# Most credentials live in the macOS keychain via the `secret` CLI; see
# docs/local-secrets.md for the full list. Use this file only for one-off
# local overrides — values here win over keychain values.
#
# To override the npm publish token for one shell session instead of pulling
# from the keychain:
#   NPM_TOKEN=npm_...
